quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  17,67,"Si lorra he…ďii on to maayo, majja …ďeen …ďe noddatno …óon, si wonaa KaŇčko [Alla] nde danndi on ka njorndi …óurno…óon, ne…ó…óaŇčke on wonii te o seeraani won'de heewu…óo jeddugol."
  17,68,"Enee, on kooli mutintaa on ka baŇče njorndi maa…óum o nula e mon damagariire [to…ďo koccu], refti he…ďantaake on fawtii…óo."
  17,69,"Ma kooli o nduttaraa on e maggo laawol goo o accita e dow mon bippooru immorde e keneeli o yoolira on sabu ko njedduno …óon ko, refti on ke…ďantaake jokkitirat…óo e dow amen cukkoowo."
  17,70,"GooŇč…óii, min teddinii …ďi…ó…ďe aadama …ďe, min ronndike …ďe ka njorndi e ka maayo min arsiki …ďe immorde e laa…ďu…ói min n …ďurni …ďe e dow ko heewi e …ďen …ďe min tagi …ďurnudee."
  17,71,"√Ďannde min noddiroyta kala yim…ďe gardii…óo ma…ď…ďe on,kala on jonnitiroyaa…óo deftere makko nde ka √Īaamo makko …ďe …óon …ďe janngay deftere ma…ď…ďe nde …ďe too√Īirtaake hay yeru gaarayol hun tamaro."
  17,72,"Kala on gon'…óo e [ngurndan aduna] ko o bun…óo, haray kaŇčko, ko ka laakara o …ďurata wumde e majjude laawol."
  17,73,"Fii kala …ďe e…ď…ďii nde …ďe fitinatmaa gaayi nde hu'unde nde min n wahayini e maa…óa fii yo a fekindo e amen ko wonaa …óun [ko min n tellini e maa] on tuma …ďe njogitoto ma sehlaajo."
  17,74,"Si tawiino min tabintinaanoma, gooŇč…óii a do'ii oo√Īa'ade e ma…ď…ďe hu'unde see…óaare."
  17,75,"On tuma min mee…óinteno cowale [lepte] ka nguurndam e cowale [lepte] kumayde refti he…ďantaake ma ballo e hoore Amen."